unbelievable and his speed was incredible since his upgrade. "You stupid 
fool you. You are neither and angel nor worthy of the name Prime. My spark 
is merged with the matrix, vector sigma and the oracle. The maximal elders 
made me to stop their experiments gone wrong, and I will do so. After I stop 
you," Recon tells him.
